	   <tr><td colspan=2>It seemed to me that this would be a nice extra piece to have around to switch out when going against casting mobs, like those in FM.&nbsp;&nbsp;I dislike being charmed and run into the giant fort, for example.  So I have it in my pack for just such occasions at the moment.<br><br>Could someone tell me precisely how Magic Resistance works?  If someone casts, say, fire magic, does it have to overcome fire AND Magic resists, or just the specific resist, in this case fire?<br><br>If so, what does magic resist save you from, and is it the most important in general? <br><br>Thanks for your time and help.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
